Author: Christopher Dannemiller <cdannemiller@nvidia.com>
Date:   Mon Apr 27 12:59:23 2026 -0700

    vkd3d: Collapse vkd3d_view AS/OMM handle aliases.

    The struct vkd3d_view union had both vk_acceleration_structure and
    vk_micromap as VkAccelerationStructureKHR - two names for one slot,
    left over from when OMM was VkMicromapEXT and the disjunction picked
    between distinct Vulkan handle types. KHR-OMM is also a
    VkAccelerationStructureKHR, making vk_micromap pure aliasing.

