Author: Hans-Kristian Arntzen <post@arntzen-software.no>
Date:   Wed May 27 18:44:01 2026 +0200

    vkd3d: Add implicit sync for BuildRTAS in more cases.

    FH6 seems to rely on this not needing to be synced for some reason ...
    At the very least, flushing RT batches when doing shading seems like a
    good idea.

    Signed-off-by: Hans-Kristian Arntzen <post@arntzen-software.no>
