    Collapses the if (using_khr_opacity_micromap) ... else dispatch in
    vkd3d_opacity_micromap_write_postbuild_info to KHR-only. The KHR
    switch (COMPACTED_SIZE / CURRENT_SIZE / SERIALIZATION) survives,
    the EXT switch (COMPACTED_SIZE / SERIALIZATION plus the
    CURRENT_SIZE-falls-through-to-zero case) is removed. Likewise the
    inner vkCmdWriteAccelerationStructuresPropertiesKHR vs
    vkCmdWriteMicromapsPropertiesEXT dispatch.

    The barrier setup in vkd3d_opacity_micromap_emit_immediate_postbuild_info
    collapses to the KHR access-mask form.

    Drop the now-orphaned VKD3D_QUERY_TYPE_INDEX_OMM_COMPACTED_SIZE and
    VKD3D_QUERY_TYPE_INDEX_OMM_SERIALIZE_SIZE macros plus their case
    clauses in d3d12_device_create_query_pool, and shrink
    VKD3D_VIRTUAL_QUERY_TYPE_COUNT from 9 to 7 to match the surviving
    RT index range. After this commit no EXT-suffixed query, pipeline-
    stage, or access-mask micromap enums remain referenced; the EXT
    build/copy/type symbols still live in opacity_micromap.c until the
    remaining EXT backends are removed.

