    vkd3d: Remove EXT backend for OMM triangles linkage.

    Reverses the EXT side of "Add KHR backend for OMM triangles linkage".
    Drops vkd3d_acceleration_structure_convert_opacity_micromap_ext,
    merges the static _khr helper and the dispatcher into a single
    non-static vkd3d_acceleration_structure_convert_opacity_micromap
    that takes a typed VkAccelerationStructureTrianglesOpacityMicromapKHR
    pointer directly.

    Three call sites collapse to KHR-only:
      - vkd3d_acceleration_structure_convert_inputs (the omm_triangles_infos
        memset and the convert_opacity_micromap call)
      - d3d12_command_list_allocate_rtas_build_info (omm_triangles_infos
        array reservation and slot pointer assignment)
      - d3d12_device_GetRaytracingAccelerationStructurePrebuildInfo (the
        anonymous union for omm_triangles_infos_stack collapses to a
        plain VkAccelerationStructureTrianglesOpacityMicromapKHR array)

    After this commit the .ext member of union vkd3d_omm_triangles_info
    has no consumers. The union itself stays until the EXT-side scaffolding
    demolition removes it.

    Signed-off-by: Christopher Dannemiller <cdannemiller@nvidia.com>
