commit c1a5408dce871b3825ae64460ff1dfe9e2b7eda9
Author: Christopher Dannemiller <cdannemiller@nvidia.com>
Date:   Sat Apr 25 12:14:52 2026 -0700

    vkd3d: Wrap opacity micromap handles in EXT/KHR union.

    Replace VkMicromapEXT in storage and signatures with
    union vkd3d_opacity_micromap, holding either the EXT handle or the
    KHR equivalent that lands with VK_KHR_opacity_micromap support.
    An application runs in exactly one OMM mode at a time, so the union
    lets the EXT and KHR paths share storage without duplication.
    No behavior change — the KHR member has no consumers yet.
