Author: Hans-Kristian Arntzen <post@arntzen-software.no>
Date:   Thu May 14 13:20:08 2026 +0200

    tests: Add exploratory test for broken table VAs.

    Signed-off-by: Hans-Kristian Arntzen <post@arntzen-software.no>
---
 tests/d3d12_descriptors.c                          | 128 +++++++++++++++++++++
 tests/d3d12_tests.h                                |   1 +
 tests/shaders/descriptors/broken_table.cs_5_1.hlsl |   9 ++
