Author: Hans-Kristian Arntzen <post@arntzen-software.no>
Date:   Wed May 6 11:11:40 2026 +0200

    vkd3d: Add descriptor heap retain workaround for Ark Ascended.

    Another very broken FSR3 integration. Really not sure who is at fault,
    games or AMD at this point, this is a pattern ...

    The descriptor heap is not covered by the existing retain workaround.
    Unsure why it was not needed for the other games we have workarounds
    for.

    Signed-off-by: Hans-Kristian Arntzen <post@arntzen-software.no>
---
 include/vkd3d.h            |  2 +-
 libs/vkd3d/command.c       | 30 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
