    vkd3d: Add internal refcount to descriptor heap.

    Signed-off-by: Hans-Kristian Arntzen <post@arntzen-software.no>
---
 libs/vkd3d/resource.c      | 25 +++++++++++++++++++------
 libs/vkd3d/vkd3d_private.h |  3 +++
