Date:   Mon Mar 23 19:36:01 2026 +0100

    vkd3d: Add RDNA1 fallback path for games that require Bary/VRS.

    Barycentrics rarely need to be stable.
    VRS tier1 can be "implemented" by just ignoring it.

    Enable this on a per-game basis to enhance compatibility with the now
    outdated RDNA1.

    Drops use of NV_fragment_barycentric. It was promoted ages ago,
    and we no longer support drivers that only expose the NV one anyway.

    Should allow Crimson Desert to be playable on RDNA1.

    Signed-off-by: Hans-Kristian Arntzen <post@arntzen-software.no>
