Author: Hans-Kristian Arntzen <post@arntzen-software.no>
Date:   Wed Jun 29 13:07:52 2022 +0200

    vkd3d: Add a crude form of alias debugging.

    Report any placed aliases which could cause issues.

    Signed-off-by: Hans-Kristian Arntzen <post@arntzen-software.no>
---
 libs/vkd3d/breadcrumbs.c   | 125 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 libs/vkd3d/heap.c          |  12 +++++
 libs/vkd3d/resource.c      |  15 ++++++
